Detailed Description

Additional setup information structure for GTI_INIT_EX().

Initialize this structure by first setting m_structRevision to GTI_INIT_INFO_REV and then set m_structLength to sizeof(GTI_INIT_INFO). Any unused members should be set to zero.

Examples:

CortexA8_Linux_Example.cpp, CortexA8_PRSC_Example.cpp, GTI_API_Example.cpp, and TargetAdapter_Example.cpp.
